author: Kuokka77
description:
"Nuova" by Jazz/Haujobb^konsumer.de, 1st at Compusphere 2025 4ch tracked music compo.
Also the soundtrack for PICO-8 demo of the same name, but it's much lower quality in the demo (demo came 1st at the same party in wild/other platforms category).
Art "Goddess of Dystopia" by Vasyl/Joker^Nah-kolor^TRSi, 1st at Xenium 2025 oldschool gfx compo.

A1200 r1D.4 audio. ProTracker 2.3F (8bitbubsy). Dolby Headphone DSP effect applied.
title: Amiga music: Jazz - Nuova (A1200🎧Dolbyfied)
